<p>
  <span class="nym">Narcissus</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>narcissus</i> 'narcissus, daffodil' from <span class="lang">Greek</span> <i>νάρκισσος</i>, of uncertain origin (cf. <span class="key">Beekes</span>, <span class="loc">p. 997</span>.).
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>In Greek mythology, the name of a son of the river god Cephissus; in history, the name of one of the 70 Disciples, a 3rd C patriarch of Jerusalem and saint, and a 4th C martyr.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


<dl>
<dt><span class="area">Spain</span></dt>
